{"tid":1399360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「急」致全體inditex及一眾零售業員工8月5日罷工","createTime":"2019-08-03T06:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T09:24:32.000Z","uid":296928,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a3f3c294be0a7f4462986da6bd470b42a8c117d","tid":1399360,"uid":296928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:49:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://partnernet.hktb.com/filemanager/intranet/pm/VisitorArrivalStatistics/ViS_Stat_C/ViS_C_2019/Tourism%20Statistics%2006%202019.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpartnernet.hktb.com%2Ffilemanager%2Fintranet%2Fpm%2FVisitorArrivalStatistics%2FViS_Stat_C%2FViS_C_2019%2FTourism%2520Statistics%252006%25202019.pdf&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsdDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=41556b3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://partnernet.hktb.com/filemanager/intranet/pm/VisitorArrivalStatistics/ViS_Stat_C/ViS_C_2019/Tourism%20Statistics%2006%202019.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年6月 中國大陸入境旅客人數400萬人 比去年同期增加10.1%<br />\n2019年上半年 2760萬人 比去年同期增加16.4%<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B10800032019MM06B0100.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statistics.gov.hk%2Fpub%2FB10800032019MM06B0100.pdf&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsdDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=0ce13cab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B10800032019MM06B0100.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年6月的零售業總銷貨價值的 臨時估計為352億元，較2018年同月下跌 6.7%<br />\n<br />\n2019年上半年的零售業 總銷貨價值的臨時估計下跌2.6%。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入境旅客人數上升 銷售額下降</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mjkqdW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mjkqdW.png&h=5990b956&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OMKkqef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOMKkqef.png&h=ee508fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h7B65eL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt